    "Applies to large sorts and watch-folder batches. Lower threshold means pacing starts sooner. Aggressive finishes faster when the Mac is warm; Gentle eases CPU and disk.": {
      "comment": "Settings: Energy section footnote.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Applies to large sorts and watch-folder batches. Lower threshold means pacing starts sooner. Aggressive finishes faster when the Mac is warm; Gentle eases CPU and disk."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "适用于大批量和文件夹批次。阈值越低意味着性能模式开始得越早。 Mac 发热时，激进模式的完成速度更快；温和模式将减轻 CPU 和磁盘的负担。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "適用於大批量和資料夾批次。閾值越低意味著起搏開始得越早。 Mac 熱時，激進的完成速度更快；溫和地減輕 CPU 和磁碟的負擔。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
