        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "當檔案名稱包含某些文字時。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When this routine has rules, they apply to files from its source folder (combined with other routines on the same path in list order).": {
      "comment": "Routine editor: rules hint.",
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此例程的规则适用于其源文件夹中的文件（同一路径上的多个例程按列表顺序合并）。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此常式的規則適用於其來源檔案夾中的檔案（同一路徑上的多個常式按列表順序合併）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
